# The government has improved the work Prozorro Market

Authors: Ukrinform (Person)

Publisher: Укринформ (Organization)

Published Time: 2023-07-04T18:24:34+03:00

Modified Time: 2023-07-04T18:24:34+03:00

Description: The Cabinet of Ministers has made changes to the specifics of the ProZorro Market, and now the only tool for the procurement will be a request for proposals. - Ukrinform.

Images: ['[630_360_16884...](https://static.ukrinform.com/photos/2023_07/thumb_files/630_360_1688484089-157.png)']

Tags: ['ProZorro', 'Уряд']

Type: Article

<!--METADATA-->

![](Images/yкринформ/2023-07-04T18-24-34-03-00/630_360_1688484089-157.png)The Cabinet of Ministers has made changes to the specifics of the ProZorro Market, and now the solemn time for the procurement will be the request of proposals.

According to Ukrinform, the relevant decision was approved by the Government on July 4, 2023, reports [press service of the Ministry of Economy](https://www.me.gov.ua/News/Detail?lang=uk-UA&id=3c957f03-c96f-4566-a6ba-265da5517782&title=UriadVdoskonalivRobotuElektronnogoKataloguProzorroMarket).

«Ми провели дослідження для того, щоб спростити роботу усіх користувачів вProzorro Market. Опитавши замовників та постачальників, ми внесли рядвдосконалень. Основна докорінна зміна полягає в тому, що тепер усі закупівлі вProzorro Market будуть відбуватися через запит пропозицій. Інструмент запитупропозицій у Prozorro Market, як і раніше дозволить замовникам швидкозакривати свої потреби без підготовки тендерної документації», - пояснилазаступник міністра економіки Надія Бігун.

**Читайте також:** [ Упродовж п’яти років у **Prozorro** .Продажі оголошували17,5 тисячі аукціонів малої приватизації ](https://www.ukrinform.ua/rubric-economy/3731322-uprodovz-pati-rokiv-u-prozorroprodazi-ogolosuvali-175-tisaci-aukcioniv-maloi-privatizacii.html)She noted that on average, such a purchase will last up to 10 days. In addition, the VZamovnik will always receive favorable offers, because he will receive an order that will be able to offer the best price

Previously, when purchases up to 100 thousand hryvnias it was possible to make direct orders of the catalog. In fact, the purchase process was similar to the purchase of a conventional online store. However, research and surveys of users have shown that these prices did not always correspond to the availability of certain goods of suppliers. Therefore, the request allows you to receive more current business proposals and better prices.

Therefore, from now on, the customers who have decided to buy the required product from ProZorromarket, regardless of the amount of purchase, should announce the request and specify the order characteristics of the order. And then the suppliers will be clearly aware of the conditions of supply and will give the current price for specific conditions of the costing.

*!(https://www.ukrinform.ua/rubric-economy/3727904-za-pat-rokiv-cerez-prozorroprodazi-derzava-otrimala-vid-privatizacii-majze-14-milardiv.html)

If the value of the goods is over UAH 500 thousand, then in this case the request must contain information about the characteristics of the product and their allowable values according to the directory profile. There is also a condition that this case should be at least two proposals from suppliers.

In order to reduce manipulation by suppliers, the requirement is required to provide a obligatory projection of the contract in the request of the proposal. The customer is also given the right to reject the winner's offer if he refuses to sign the contract and proceed to the consideration of the next one.

*!(https://www.ukrinform.ua/rubric-economy/3726748-u-travni-cerez-prozorro-opublikuvali-zakupivel-na-121-milard.html)In the new order of procurement, the concept of procurement profile is removed, instead, the concept of technical specification is introduced. This should be removed by some foolish understanding that has arisen when communicating the product.

As reported, Prozorro Market administrators are three centralized organizations. Professional purchases are filled with consumer catalogs, medical procurement of Ukraine - medicines and medical products, SE "Ukrainian Special Systems" - computer equipment and software. Today, the range of Prozorro Market has about 90 thousand works of 3 thousand skilled suppliers.

